==Hindi==
===Personal pronoun===
'''हम''' (ham)
# [[We]] (first person plural, nominative case) (Singular: [[मैं]] or हम in alternate usage)
#:Example: "हम हैं" - "We are"
# [[I]] (the first person singular pronoun)

====Usage====
Because हम can mean both we and I, sometimes [[हम]] [[लोग]] is used to specifically denote the plural. Usually context makes it clear when हम is being used for we or for I. It is inflected and used grammatically the same for both meanings.

====Inflection====
{| 
| object || '''[[हम]]''' (ham)
|-
| reflexive || '''[[अपना]]''' (apnā)
|-
| possessive || '''[[हमारा]]''' (hamārā)
|}

